ini-parser provides header-only INI file parsing.

Usage:
    find_package(ini-parser CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE ini-parser::ini-parser)

Example:
    #include <ini-parser/ini_parser.hpp>
    ini::parser cfg;
    cfg.load("config.ini");
    auto val = cfg.get("section", "key");
    cfg.set("section", "key", "new_value");
    cfg.save("config.ini");
